data.description:
Welcome home! This well-tended 3 bed/ 2 bath home is nestled in a quiet neighborhood, and welcomes you in with hard wood floors and so much light!  The kitchen has been updated with new counters, fixtures and appliances. There is a full bathroom on the upper level and two bedrooms with a living room that borders the eat-in kitchen. The lower garden level is also full of light and has been freshly painted. There is a spacious great room (which could be split into an additional bedroom), 3/4 bath, laundry/utility room, garage access, and a lower level bedroom. The home has a HUGE backyard with mature trees, a deck, a patio, and grill that is hooked up to a natural gas line. Double parking - a one car garage AND a one car attached carport. Roof is 6 years old, sewer was scoped 1/12/24 and has no issues. The HVAC system is 4 years old - furnace, air conditioner and water heater. Electric box was replaced in 2010. All the big things are done! The home is located just blocks from shopping, dining and has easy highway access. This gem is located within walking distance of multiple schools and around the corner from Wyco park, STEM school, and open spaces. And NO HOA! This won't last long!

SHOWINGS BEGIN February 1
